(E'#ArticlesAwaitingReviewersText',E'default',E'<p>The preprints that appear below are being evaluated at {{longname}}. If you are interested in reviewing one of these preprints, you can click on the blue \'WILLING TO REVIEW\' button of the corresponding line. The recommender handling this preprint will accept or decline your review proposal. In case of acceptance, you will receive a message with details on how to post your review. Thanks for your help!</p>'),
